channel.title: Eclipse-Rsps release 3.0 desert agility, New fun pk teams, dicing, 200+ DL'S!
channel.description: Welcome to Eclipse-Rsps 3.0 release. This release has everything that v2 had, and more. v2 had dicing, new donor zone, and more. To look at this release please visit ----> http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,530284.0.html 10 DL's [X] 50 DL's [X] 100 DL's [X] 200 DL's [X] 300 DL's [] ~Enjoy~ [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/1-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/2-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/3-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/4-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/5-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/6-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/7-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/8-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/9-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/10-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/11-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/12-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/13-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/14-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/15-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/16-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/171.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/18-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/19-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/20-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/21-1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i932.photobucket.com/albums/ad162/dominatorz93/22-1.jpg[/img] There is 100% dicing, frost dragon teleport, holiday events for every holidy, and a duel arena duping glitch fixed. ~for the noobs~ 1. Change the ip in server.java 2. If you use rspscoding or rs-ps then the server will be compatable with hybrid pvp v3 loader. 3. If your using rs-ps or rspscoding webclient, the custom tab, and new hitmarks will not show up in the webclient, but all the new items like the bows will work and there specials will as well. ~enjoy~ Source ~ http://www.mediafire.com/?l9mx6s6rtp7jvol client ~ http://www.mediafire.com/?wnxd6tnmm1b0f5h hybrid pvp/PI- 65% Myself 35% If you're going to host this please message me, I'd love to play.
